quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  29,1,Alif Laam Miim
  29,2,"Ese abantu bibaza ko bazabaho batageragezwa kubera ko bavuze bati\"Twaremeye"
  29,3,"Kandi rwose twagerageje ababayeho mbere yabo; kugira ngo Allah agaragaze abanyakuri, ndetse anagaragaze abanyabinyoma"
  29,4,Ese babandi bakora ibikorwa bibi bibwira ko bazaducika?Rwose ibyo bibwira ni bibi
  29,5,"Uwizera kuzahura na Allah, mu by’ukuri, igihe ntarengwa Allah yagennye kiregereje. Kandi we ni Uwumva bihebuje, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  29,6,"Kandi uzarwana mu nzira ya (Allah), uwo azaba yigiriye ubwe. Mu by’ukuri, Allaharihagije ntacyo akeneyeku biremwa byose"
  29,7,"Kandi babandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, rwose tuzabababarira ibyaha, tunabagororere bihebuje kubera ibyo bakoraga"
  29,8,"Twanategetse umuntu kugirira neza ababyeyi be; ariko nibaramuka baguhatiye kumbangikanya n’ibyo udafitiye ubumenyi, ntuzabumvire. Iwanjye ni ho garukiro ryanyu, maze nkazababwira ibyo mwajyaga mukora"
  29,9,"Na babandi bemeye bakanakora ibyiza, rwose tuzabinjiza mu ntungane (mu ijuru)"
  29,10,"No mu bantu hari abavuga bati \"Twemeye Allah!\" Ariko batotezwa bazira Allah, bagafata ibigeragezo by’abantu nk’ibihano bya Allah(bagata ukwemera); nyamara ubutabazi buturutse kwa Nyagasani wawe bwagera (ku bemeramana), (indyarya) zikavuga ziti \"Mu by’ukuri, twari kumwe na mwe\". Ese Allah si we uzi neza ibiri mu bituza by’ibiremwa byose"
  29,11,Kandi Allahazi neza abemeye ndetse azi neza indyarya
  29,12,"Na babandi bahakanye babwiye abemeye bati \"Nimukurikire inzira yacu, tuzirengera ibyaha byanyu\". Nyamara ntibazigera birengera ibyaha byabo, ahubwo mu by’ukuri ni abanyabinyoma"
  29,13,Kandi rwose bazirengera imitwaro yabo hamwe n’imitwaro (y’abo bayobeje) yiyongereye ku yabo. Ndetse rwose ku munsi w’imperuka bazabazwa ibyo bahimbaga
  29,14,"Kandi rwose twohereje Nuhu ku bantu be, abana nabo imyaka igihumbi iburaho mirongo itanu (abahamagarira kwemera Allah, ntibamwumvira). Nuko barimburwa n’umwuzure ari inkozi z’ibibi"
  29,15,"Nuko turamurokora we n’abari mu nkuge, maze tubigira ikimenyetso ku biremwa byose"
  29,16,"(Unibuke yewe Muhamadi) ubwo Ibrahimu yabwiraga abantu be ati \"Nimusenge Allah munamutinye. Ibyo ni byo byiza kuri mwe, iyaba mwari mubizi"
  29,17,"Rwose ibyo musenga bitari Allah ni ibigirwamana, maze mugahimba ikinyoma (mubyita Imana). Mu by’ukuri, ibyo musenga bitari Allah, si byo bigenga amafunguro yanyu. Bityo nimushakire amafunguro kwa Allah, mumusenge kandi mumushimire. Iwe ni ho muzasubizwa"
  29,18,"Kandi nimuramuka muhinyuye (intumwa, mumenye ko) rwose imiryango (umat) yabayeho mbere yanyu nayo yahinyuye (intumwa zayo). Nta n’ikindi intumwa ishinzwe usibye gusohoza ubutumwa bugaragara"
  29,19,"Ese (abahakanyi) ntibabona uko Allahyaremye ibiremwa (bitari biriho) hanyuma akazanabigarura (nyuma yo gupfa)? Mu by’ukuri, ibyo kuri Allah biroroshye"
  29,20,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"Nimutambagire ku isi maze murebe uko (Allah) yaremye ibiremwa (bitari biriho), hanyuma Allahakazongera kurema bwa nyuma (ku izuka). Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Ushobora byose"
  29,21,"Ahana uwo ashatse, akanagirira impuhwe uwo ashatse; kandi iwe ni ho muzagarurwa"
  29,22,Kandi ntabwo mwananira (Allah) haba ku isi cyangwa mu kirere. Nta n’undi murinzi cyangwa umutabazi mufite utari Allah
  29,23,"Na babandi bahakanye amagambo ya Allah no kuzahura na we, ni bo bataye icyizere cyo kuzabona impuhwe zanjye, kandi ni nabo bazahanishwa ibihano bibabaza"
  29,24,"Nta kindi cyari igisubizo cy’abantu be (Ibrahimu) uretse kuvuga bati \"Mumwice cyangwa mumutwike!\" Maze Allah amurokora umuriro. Mu by’ukuri, muri ibyo harimo ibimenyetso ku bantu bemera"
  29,25,"Nuko (Ibrahimu) aravuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, mwishyiriyeho ibigirwamana mumwanya wa Allah, kugira ngo mushimangire urukundo hagati yanyu mu buzima bw’isi. Nyamara ku munsi w’imperuka bamwe bazihakana abandi, banavumane. Kandi ubuturo bwanyu buzaba umuriro, ndetse nta n’abatabazi muzagira"